title: TI 84 Plus CE Introduction
description:
This is an introduction to the TI-84 Plus CE calculator from Texas Instruments.  I purchased this from The Bach Company (www.bachcompany.com) and it was delivered last night.  

Key Features:
* Slim Design
* 154K RAM, the most for any version of the TI-83/84 by far
* Color Screen
* Rechargeable Battery, which uses the standard Mini USB cable
* Same interface to the TI-84+ family, it is ready to go right out of the box

Caution: this movie was done early in the morning and I had not had my morning coffee.  

Full review to be posted soon on my blog, edspi31415.blogspot.com.
